{"id":669563894,"lang":"swift","time":"3 months, 1 week","timestamp":1648545106,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"10 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/669563894/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Second Largest Digit in a String","memory":"14.6 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    func secondHighest(_ s: String) -> Int {\n        var hashMap: [Character : Bool] = [:]\n        \n        for char in s { hashMap[char] = true }\n        \n        var largestDigit = -1\n        \n        for digit in 0...9 {\n            let char = Character(String(digit))\n            if hashMap[char] != nil {\n                largestDigit = max(largestDigit, digit)\n            }\n        }\n        \n        var secondLargestDigit = -1\n        \n        if largestDigit != -1 {\n            for digit in 0...9 {\n                let char = Character(String(digit))\n                if hashMap[char] != nil, digit < largestDigit  {\n                    secondLargestDigit = max(secondLargestDigit, digit)\n                }\n            }\n        }\n        \n        return secondLargestDigit\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"second-largest-digit-in-a-string"}
